-slate-900\" href=\"/convert/webp-to-jpg\"><p class=\"mb-3 text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-blue-300\">Image Tools</p><h3 class=\"mb-2 text-xl font-bold\">WEBP to JPG</h3><p class=\"text-sm leading-6 text-slate-400\">Convert WEBP images into JPG format online for free.</p></a><a class=\"rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-slate-900/70 p-6 transition hover:border-blue-500/60 hover:bg-slate-900\" href=\"/convert/image-to-pdf\"><p class=\"mb-3 text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-blue-300\">PDF Tools</p><h3 class=\"mb-2 text-xl font-bold\">Image to PDF</h3><p class=\"text-sm leading-6 text-slate-400\">Convert JPG, PNG or WEBP images to PDF online for free.</p></a><a class=\"rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-slate-900/70 p-6 transition hover:border-blue-500/60 hover:bg-slate-900\" href=\"/convert/pdf-to-image\"><p class=\"mb-3 text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-blue-300\">PDF Tools</p><h3 class=\"mb-2 text-xl font-bold\">PDF to Image</h3><p class=\"text-sm leading-6 text-slate-400\">Convert PDF pages to PNG images online for free.</p></a><a class=\"rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-slate-900/70 p-6 transition hover:border-blue-500/60 hover:bg-slate-900\" href=\"/convert/pdf-merge\"><p class=\"mb-3 text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-blue-300\">PDF Tools</p><h3 class=\"mb-2 text-xl font-bold\">PDF Merge</h3><p class=\"text-sm leading-6 text-slate-400\">Merge multiple PDF files into one PDF online for free.</p></a><a class=\"rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-slate-900/70 p-6 transition hover:border-blue-500/60 hover:bg-slate-900\" href=\"/convert/video-metadata\"><p class=\"mb-3 text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-blue-300\">Video Tools</p><h3 class=\"mb-2 text-xl font-bold\">Video Metadata Viewer</h3><p class=\"text-sm leading-6 text-slate-400\">View MP4, WEBM and MOV metadata including duration, file size and resolution.</p></a><a class=\"rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-sla