ions per day and no account required.</p></a><a class=\"rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-slate-900/70 p-6 transition hover:border-blue-500/60 hover:bg-slate-900\" href=\"/convert/tiktok-hashtag-generator\"><p class=\"mb-3 text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-blue-300\">Social Media Tools</p><h3 class=\"mb-2 text-xl font-bold\">TikTok Hashtag Generator</h3><p class=\"text-sm leading-6 text-slate-400\">Free Gemini-powered AI generation with three generations per day and no account required.</p></a><a class=\"rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-slate-900/70 p-6 transition hover:border-blue-500/60 hover:bg-slate-900\" href=\"/convert/instagram-caption-generator\"><p class=\"mb-3 text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-blue-300\">Social Media Tools</p><h3 class=\"mb-2 text-xl font-bold\">Instagram Caption Generator</h3><p class=\"text-sm leading-6 text-slate-400\">Free Gemini-powered AI generation with three generations per day and no account required.</p></a><a class=\"rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-slate-900/70 p-6 transition hover:border-blue-500/60 hover:bg-slate-900\" href=\"/convert/remove-image-metadata\"><p class=\"mb-3 text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-blue-300\">Image Tools</p><h3 class=\"mb-2 text-xl font-bold\">Remove Image Metadata</h3><p class=\"text-sm leading-6 text-slate-400\">Remove most EXIF and embedded metadata from JPG, PNG or WEBP images using a private browser-based canvas re-export.</p></a><a class=\"rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-slate-900/70 p-6 transition hover:border-blue-500/60 hover:bg-slate-900\" href=\"/convert/image-color-picker\"><p class=\"mb-3 text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-blue-300\">Image Tools</p><h3 class=\"mb-2 text-xl font-bold\">Image Color Picker</h3><p class=\"text-sm leading-6 text-slate-400\">Pick any pixel color from a JPG, PNG or WEBP image and copy HEX, RGB or HSL values.</p></a><a class=\"rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-slate-900/70 p-6 transition hover:border-blue-500/60 hover:bg-slate-900\" href=\"/convert/avif-to-jpg\"><p class=\"mb-3 text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-blue-300\">Image Tools</p><h3 class=\"mb-2 text-xl font-bold\">AVIF to JPG</h3><p class=\"text-sm leading-6 text-slate-400\">Convert AVIF images to JPG in your browser using native image decoding.</p></a></div></div></section><section class=\"border-y border-white/10 bg-slate-900/40 px-6 py-16\"><div class=\"mx-auto max-w-6xl\"><p class=\"text-sm font-bold uppercase text-emerald-300\">Free AI <!-- -->·<!-- --> 3/day</p><h2 class=\"mt-3 text-3xl font-black\">Create faster with free AI tools</h2><p class=\"mt-4 max-w-2xl leading-7 text-slate-400\">Generate captions, titles, hashtags, emails, summaries, bios and content ideas with Gemini. No account or API key required.</p><a class=\"mt-6 inline-flex rounded-xl bg-blue-600 px-5 py-3 font-semibold text-white hover:bg-blue-500\" href=\"/ai-tools\">Explore Free AI Tools</a></div></section><section class=\"px-6 py-20\"><div class=\"mx-auto max-w-7xl\"><div class=\"mb-10 max-w-3xl\"><h2 class=\"mb-4 text-4xl font-black tracking-tight md:text-5xl\">Why use A2ZConvertor?</h2><p class=\"text-lg text-slate-400\">A2ZConvertor brings <!-- -->51<!-- --> tools across <!-- -->6<!-- --> <!-- -->categories into one clean, fast file workflow.</p></div><div class=\"grid gap-5 md:grid-cols-3\"><div class=\"rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-slate-900/70 p-6\"><h3 class=\"mb-3 text-xl font-bold\">Browser-first processing</h3><p class=\"leading-7 text-slate-400\">Many tools run directly in your browser, keeping everyday file tasks fast and private where possible.</p></div><div class=\"rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-slate-900/70 p-6\"><h3 class=\"mb-3 text-xl font-bold\">No account required</h3><p class=\"leading-7 text-slate-400\">Open a tool, process your file and download the result without creating an account.</p></div><div class=\"rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-slate-900/70 p-6\"><h3 class=\"mb-3 text-xl font-bold\">Built for launch workflows</h3><p class=\"leading-7 text-slate-400\">Use focused converters, compressors and editors for images, PDFs, audio and video from one searchable place.</p></div></div></div></section><section class=\"px-6 py-20\"><div class=\"mx-auto max-w-4xl\"><h2 class=\"mb-8 text-4xl font-black tracking-tight md:text-5xl\">Homepage FAQ</h2><div class=\"space-y-4\"><div class=\"rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-slate-900/70 p-6\"><h3 class=\"mb-2 text-xl font-bold\">Is A2ZConvertor free to use?</h3><p class=\"leading-7 text-slate-400\">Yes. The current tools are free to use online without account registration.</p></div><div class=\"rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-slate-900/70 p-6\"><h3 class=\"mb-2 text-xl font-bold\">Are files uploaded to a server?</h3><p class=\"leading-7 text-slate-400\">Many tools process files directly in your browser. Some workflows depend on browser support, and each tool page explains important output limitations where needed.</p></div><div class=\"rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-slate-900/70 p-6\"><h3 class=\"mb-2 text-xl font-bold\">Can I request a new tool?</h3><p class=\"leading-7 text-slate-400\">Yes. Use the Request a Tool page to suggest new converters, editors or improvements to existing tools.</p></div><div class=\"rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-slate-900/70 p-6\"><h3 class=\"mb-2 text-xl font-bold\">Which tool categories are available?</h3><p class=\"leading-7 text-slate-400\">A2ZConvertor currently includes image, PDF, audio and video tools, with more launch-ready utilities planned.</p></div></div></div></section><footer class=\"border-t border-white/10 px-6 py-16\"><div class=\"mx-auto mb-12 max-w-7xl\"><section class=\"rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-slate-900/70 p-5\"><div class=\"\"><h2 class=\"text-xl font-black\">Get new free tools and productivity tips.</h2><p class=\"mt-3 max-w-2xl leading-7 text-slate-400\">Be first to know when we launch new converters, PDF tools and browser-based productivity tools.</p><form class=\"mt-5 flex gap-3 flex-col\"><label class=\"sr-only\" for=\"_R_3qnlb_\">Email address</label><input id=\"_R_3qnlb_\" type=\"email\" required=\"\" autoComplete=\"email\" placeholder=\"you@example.com\" class=\"min-w-0 flex-1 rounded-xl border border-white/10 bg-slate-950 px-4 py-3 text-white outline-none focus:border-blue-500\" name=\"email\" value=\"\"/><input type=\"hidden\" name=\"source\" value=\"a2zconvertor\"/><button type=\"submit\" class=\"rounded-xl bg-blue-600 px-5 py-3 font-semibold text-white hover:bg-blue-500\">Join by email</button></form><p class=\"mt-3 text-xs leading-5 text-slate-500\">No newsletter provider is connected yet. This opens your email app; we do not fake a stored subscription.</p></div></section></div><div class=\"mx-auto grid max-w-7xl gap-10 md:grid-cols-4\"><div><h3 class=\"mb-4 text-2xl font-black\">A2Z<span class=\"text-blue-500\">Convertor</span></h3><p class=\"text-slate-400\">Free online tools to convert, compress and edit files quickly.</p></div><div><h4 class=\"mb-4 font-bold\">Categories</h4><ul class=\"space-y-2 text-slate-400\"><li><a class=\"transition hover:text-white\" href=\"/tools\">All Tools</a></li><li><a class=\"transition hover:text-white\" href=\"/image-tools\">Image Tools</a></li><li><a class=\"transition hover:text-white\" href=\"/pdf-tools\">PDF Tools</a></li><li><a class=\"transition hover:text-white\" href=\"/video-tools\">Video Tools</a></li><li><a class=\"transition hover:text-white\" href=\"/audio-tools\">Audio Tools</a></li><li><a class=\"transition hover:text-white\" href=\"/text-tools\">Text Tools</a></li><li><a class=\"transition hover:text-white\" href=\"/social-media-tools\">Social Media Tools</a></li></ul></div><div><h4 class=\"mb-4 font-bold\">Popular Tools</h4><ul class=\"space-y-2 text-slate-400\"><li><a class=\"transition hover:text-white\" href=\"/convert/jpg-to-png\">JPG to PNG</a></li><li><a class=\"tran